---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | GoldShore" description="Terms of service overview">
  <section class="gs-section gs-blueprint-bg gs-section--padded">
    <div class="gs-container">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p>
        GoldShore.ai engagements are delivered through statement-of-work based
        contracts with explicit milestones, response windows, and ownership terms.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Service scope is defined per engagement with acceptance criteria.</li>
        <li>Operational support windows and escalation paths are documented before kickoff.</li>
        <li>Security and data handling obligations are included in the governing agreement.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For policy and entity disclosures, visit
        <a href="/legal/compliance">Legal &amp; Compliance</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
